    "description": "用你的鞭子保护蛋！鞭打敌人以击败他们。如果敌人太多，你甚至可以鞭打蛋来召唤士兵。但要小心，因为蛋里有一个Boss，每次受到伤害都会缩短孵化时间。当它孵化时，你需要击败Boss。<br><br>- 击败敌人的波浪，收集金币以升级你的角色<br>- 收集卷轴以获取独特的技能<br>- 你可以鞭打蛋来召唤士兵。士兵会帮助你击败敌人<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146900/extras/dacf62b149bc79b4e0eb133a17020fd2.poster.avif?t=1731351290\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146900/extras/dacf62b149bc79b4e0eb133a17020fd2.webm?t=1731351290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146900/extras/dacf62b149bc79b4e0eb133a17020fd2.mp4?t=1731351290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br><br>- 蛋会随时间孵化，但在受到伤害时，它会更快孵化。当它孵化时，Boss会出现，并且会开始一场艰难的Boss战斗<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146900/extras/399f65fab42acf1077c0cc61a24e4525.poster.avif?t=1731351290\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146900/extras/399f65fab42acf1077c0cc61a24e4525.webm?t=1731351290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146900/extras/399f65fab42acf1077c0cc61a24e4525.mp4?t=1731351290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146900/extras/b29f0749bc6a50c494f29bd7c416918c.poster.avif?t=1731351290\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146900/extras/b29f0749bc6a50c494f29bd7c416918c.webm?t=1731351290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146900/extras/b29f0749bc6a50c494f29bd7c416918c.mp4?t=1731351290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br><br>- 尽可能延迟Boss的出现，并变得更强大以击败它<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146900/extras/e0be62984012f56076482893e6050173.poster.avif?t=1731351290\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146900/extras/e0be62984012f56076482893e6050173.webm?t=1731351290\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146900/extras/e0be62984012f56076482893e6050173.mp4?t=1731351290\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.",
